room_title: Escape room "60-to-Life" by Escapades in Sioux Falls
room_address: 3313 S Western Ave Sioux Falls, SD 57105
room_description: Traveling through a small country town late at night you are pulled over by the local sheriff. You have no idea why, but your entire group has been arrested. He takes you back to the small town jail but instead of locking you up in the regular cells, you are led to the basement and locked up there. As you look around you realize this may be your final trip if you do not escape!
